snippet.title: ALGEBRA QUESTIONS: WHY ARE LINES 180 DEGREES?
snippet.description:
Join us on this video lesson where we answer another famous algebra questions: why do straight lines measure 180 degrees (why are straight lines 180 degrees)? This lesson features Jason Kidd and his famous "we're going to turn this team around 360 degrees" quote! For more MashUp Math content, visit http://www.mashupmath.com and join our free mailing list! :)

This lesson answers the questions: Why is a straight line 180 degrees? How many degrees are in a straight line? What is a linear pair? What are supplementary angles?

Be sure to join our mailing list at http://www.mashupmath.com
